00:07:40.230 --> 00:07:43.230
That's a very difficult thing to do.

00:07:43.230 --> 00:07:53.230
We don't want our relatives to choke because we're forcing too much information or with too much force or power.

00:07:53.230 --> 00:07:59.230
Instead, we want our relatives to feel refreshed by the truth.

00:07:59.230 --> 00:08:08.230
Well, whether our relatives feel choked or refreshed will really depend on how we go about explaining the truth to them.

00:08:08.230 --> 00:08:15.230
So be tactful and speak to them in a loving way that will stimulate their interest.

00:08:15.230 --> 00:08:18.230
Let's go to that third point.

00:08:18.230 --> 00:08:24.230
